{"tid":220769,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴研究推出月票或分四類","createTime":"2017-04-28T08:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T08:03:18.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e55a4538c75d09a6c9ff2281f98c611803560656","tid":220769,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:03:18.000Z","msg":"九巴正研究推出月票計劃，消息指月票初步會分四款，分別為來往新界東和新界西，及過海與不過海，其中來往新界東的月票價格會較低，整體方案有待九巴與運輸署磋商。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員劉國勳說，九巴將於下月五日前，向運輸及房屋局提交月票方案，如獲政府接納，相信最快可於今年內推出。他說，月票主要針對長途乘客。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=936836&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D936836%26csid%3D261_341&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdeargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=1b5813a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=936836&amp;csid=261_341</a>"}]}